item.title: Speaking at SharePoint Fest DC 2019
item.author: vbiret+blog@outlook.com (Vincent Biret)
item.description: SharePoint Fest Washington DC 2018 is happening from April 29th to May the 3rd. This event will feature 2 days pre-conference workshops and 3 days of conference. You can find more information about it on the website.
